<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢٢٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6740">‌هَنَّادٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4092">‌عَبْدَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">‌عُبَيْدِ اللهِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">‌نَافِعٍ </a>: «أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">‌ابْنَ عُمَرَ </a>كَانَ يَلْبَسُ خَاتَمَهُ فِي يَدِهِ الْيُسْرَى.»<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>